#  Series df
class Characteristic:
    def __init__(self,X,ty):
        self.__data = X
        self.__variables = [x for x in set(self.__data)]
        self.__count=len(set(self.__data))
        self.__type=ty
        
    def getvariables(self):
        return self.__variables
    
    def getcount(self):
        return self.__count
    
    def trans(self):
        arr = []
        for ty in self.__variables[:-1]:
            temp = []
            for va in self.__data:
                if va==ty:temp.append(1)
                else:temp.append(0)
            arr.append(temp)
        df = pd.DataFrame(arr)
        df=df.T
        df.columns=[str(x)+"("+self.__type+")" for x in self.__variables[:-1]]
        return df

    for j in range(4):

        m=min(df_fain2.iloc[:,k])
        M=max(df_fain2.iloc[:,k])
